1
00:00:05,654 --> 00:00:08,350
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,424 --> 00:00:12,292
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,361 --> 00:00:16,354
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,698 --> 00:00:19,189
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,268 --> 00:00:23,329
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,405 --> 00:00:27,364
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,844 --> 00:00:33,577
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,283 --> 00:00:37,252
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,688 --> 00:00:41,781
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,524 --> 00:00:43,821
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,159 --> 00:00:46,719
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,770 --> 00:01:00,140
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,342 --> 00:01:01,502
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,577 --> 00:01:05,377
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,714 --> 00:01:10,913
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,186 --> 00:01:12,517
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,588 --> 00:01:13,987
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,056 --> 00:01:20,325
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:30,053 --> 00:01:32,044
Hinata Hyuga vs. Neji Hyuga

20
00:01:32,699 --> 00:01:36,294
Withdraw! You're not suited
to being a Shinobi.

21
00:01:39,906 --> 00:01:42,807
You don't have the privilege of
deciding what a person is like, stupid!

22
00:01:43,209 --> 00:01:45,268
Hinata, give it to him!

23
00:01:49,582 --> 00:01:50,310
<i>Naruto...</i>

24
00:01:51,951 --> 00:01:53,680
Don't just take it! Argue back!

25
00:01:54,187 --> 00:01:56,121
I'm getting irritated watching this!

26
00:02:01,027 --> 00:02:01,857
<i>Naruto...</i>

27
00:02:04,764 --> 00:02:05,628
<i>Thank you!</i>

28
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:08,562
<i>The expression of her eyes</i>
<i>has changed...</i>

29
00:02:10,070 --> 00:02:11,833
So you're not going to withdraw?

30
00:02:11,905 --> 00:02:13,338
I'm not taking responsibility
for what happens...

31
00:02:14,841 --> 00:02:15,705
<i>I don't want to run away!</i>

32
00:02:17,577 --> 00:02:18,339
Byakugan!

33
00:02:22,082 --> 00:02:24,880
Brother Neji! I challenge you!

34
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,064
<i>Here!</i>

35
00:02:41,601 --> 00:02:47,471
<i>A Failure Stands Tall!</i>

36
00:03:28,782 --> 00:03:30,409
As I thought, this is the extent of it...

37
00:03:31,251 --> 00:03:32,548
the head family's power!

38
00:03:33,586 --> 00:03:34,814
What the?!

39
00:03:35,221 --> 00:03:37,951
But Hinata laid a perfect strike!

40
00:03:42,095 --> 00:03:42,993
<i>N-Not yet...</i>

41
00:03:55,642 --> 00:03:56,666
<i>What's with this guy...!</i>

42
00:03:59,646 --> 00:04:00,476
<i>I-It can't be...</i>

43
00:04:01,915 --> 00:04:02,711
<i>Well, now...</i>

44
00:04:02,949 --> 00:04:07,716
<i>I guess this is why he's called</i>
<i>the most gifted of the Hyuga clan yet.</i>

45
00:04:27,006 --> 00:04:30,669
Y-You mean... All this time...?

46
00:04:30,910 --> 00:04:34,471
That's right! I can see
the Chakra Points.

47
00:04:34,814 --> 00:04:36,611
W-What is he talking about?!

48
00:04:37,383 --> 00:04:38,782
On the Chakra Network...

49
00:04:39,185 --> 00:04:42,348
there are 361 energy centers
or Chakra opening,

50
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:45,355
each about the size
of the head of a pin.

51
00:04:46,693 --> 00:04:47,819
They're called Chakra Points.

52
00:04:49,095 --> 00:04:55,728
Theoretically, hitting one directly
can halt or increase Chakra flow,

53
00:04:56,169 --> 00:04:59,570
enabling one to gain complete control over
an opponent's flow of Chakra.

54
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:02,635
Just so you know,

55
00:05:03,309 --> 00:05:07,370
not even my Sharingan
can see Chakra Points!

56
00:05:09,282 --> 00:05:11,477
Having the penetrating eye
is one thing,

57
00:05:11,551 --> 00:05:13,451
but to hit it so accurately like
that during a match,

58
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,418
well, that's just...

59
00:05:27,267 --> 00:05:28,131
Lady Hinata...

60
00:05:28,668 --> 00:05:31,136
What we have here is an unchangeable
difference in abilities.

61
00:05:31,704 --> 00:05:34,195
It's what distinguishes
the elite from the failure.

62
00:05:37,477 --> 00:05:39,468
It is brute, unalterable fact.

63
00:05:40,179 --> 00:05:42,044
You were destined to regret having said

64
00:05:42,382 --> 00:05:45,476
that you don't want to run anymore,
the instant you said it.

65
00:05:46,386 --> 00:05:49,219
And now, you must have
abandoned yourself to despair!

66
00:05:52,292 --> 00:05:54,021
This is your ultimatum...

67
00:05:55,662 --> 00:05:56,651
Withdraw!

68
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,093
I-I...

69
00:06:08,641 --> 00:06:09,573
I-I meant it...

70
00:06:11,644 --> 00:06:13,305
and am... sticking by...

71
00:06:17,517 --> 00:06:18,575
every word...

72
00:06:19,953 --> 00:06:20,783
<i>Hinata...</i>

73
00:06:22,789 --> 00:06:23,721
I said!

74
00:06:24,924 --> 00:06:26,448
<i>I'm not gonna run away!</i>

75
00:06:28,695 --> 00:06:32,131
Because that's... my Way of Ninja!

76
00:06:57,724 --> 00:07:01,285
I had no idea... Hinata was this tough...

77
00:07:01,394 --> 00:07:02,759
She's a lot like you.

78
00:07:03,696 --> 00:07:07,359
Come to think of it...
She's always watching you.

79
00:07:07,634 --> 00:07:08,100
Huh?

80
00:07:12,939 --> 00:07:13,871
<i>Hinata...</i>

81
00:07:21,581 --> 00:07:22,513
Bring it on!

82
00:07:33,393 --> 00:07:34,826
<i>She has reached her limit.</i>

83
00:07:35,962 --> 00:07:38,123
<i>One more blow and...</i>

84
00:07:48,775 --> 00:07:51,039
<i>Neji's hits to Hinata's Chakra Points</i>

85
00:07:51,511 --> 00:07:54,036
<i>have completely halted</i>
<i>her flow of Chakra.</i>

86
00:07:55,381 --> 00:07:58,373
<i>That means she can no longer</i>
<i>send Chakra</i>

87
00:07:58,451 --> 00:08:01,079
<i>into her opponent's body</i>
<i>to fight in the Gentle Fist.</i>

88
00:08:02,588 --> 00:08:04,453
<i>This match is as good as over.</i>

89
00:08:05,758 --> 00:08:08,693
<i>But I never imagined there would</i>
<i>be someone this powerful...</i>

90
00:08:09,162 --> 00:08:13,496
<i>I'm afraid even our Sasuke</i>
<i>is no match for him.</i>

91
00:08:15,101 --> 00:08:18,229
<i>It looks as if Neji may very well</i>
<i>take this Exam.</i>

92
00:08:18,805 --> 00:08:20,568
<i>It's going to take more than what</i>
<i>this girl has to bring him down.</i>

93
00:08:32,051 --> 00:08:33,712
L-Look at those eyes...

94
00:08:34,353 --> 00:08:38,949
Is he going to try to kill her?
No, no, that's absurd.

95
00:08:39,225 --> 00:08:40,658
Doesn't it seem that...

96
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:42,618
Neji's strength is somehow
against the rules?

97
00:08:43,429 --> 00:08:44,361
He's just too powerful...

98
00:08:45,198 --> 00:08:45,857
I mean it!

99
00:08:50,436 --> 00:08:53,234
Go, Hinata!

100
00:08:57,009 --> 00:08:57,737
<i>Naruto...</i>

101
00:08:59,445 --> 00:09:01,413
<i>Strength has come back</i>
<i>into her eyes...</i>

102
00:09:03,616 --> 00:09:05,174
<i>I've been watching you...</i>

103
00:09:11,023 --> 00:09:13,617
<i>I've been watching you closely</i>
<i>for many years now!</i>

104
00:09:18,464 --> 00:09:19,431
<i>Why I wonder...?</i>

105
00:09:24,804 --> 00:09:26,738
<i>Next up is Naruto Uzumaki!</i>

106
00:09:27,273 --> 00:09:29,332
<i>What a pain!</i>

107
00:09:29,642 --> 00:09:31,303
<i>It's all your fault!</i>

108
00:09:31,711 --> 00:09:32,905
<i>Like I care!</i>

109
00:09:35,648 --> 00:09:36,637
<i>Okay!</i>

110
00:09:38,551 --> 00:09:41,179
Naruto... d-do your best.

111
00:09:42,054 --> 00:09:42,850
<i>Transformation!</i>

112
00:09:45,324 --> 00:09:46,723
<i>I don't know why, but...</i>

113
00:09:58,905 --> 00:10:01,339
<i>I am Naruto Uzumaki!</i>

114
00:10:01,507 --> 00:10:03,600
<i>I'm not about to lose to</i>
<i>the likes of any of you!</i>

115
00:10:03,743 --> 00:10:05,370
<i>Is that perfectly clear?!</i>

116
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:14,316
<i>I'm not about to lose to</i>
<i>the likes of any of you? Yeah, right!</i>

117
00:10:14,987 --> 00:10:15,715
<i>That idiot.</i>

118
00:10:16,255 --> 00:10:19,190
<i>He made a roomful of enemies</i>
<i>in the space of an instant.</i>

119
00:10:23,663 --> 00:10:25,096
<i>When I watch Naruto...</i>

120
00:10:30,303 --> 00:10:31,565
<i>Naruto, stand up!</i>

121
00:10:39,111 --> 00:10:42,410
<i>If you compete with me</i>
<i>for the name of Hokage...</i>

122
00:10:43,115 --> 00:10:46,516
<i>You... will be the loser!</i>

123
00:10:48,521 --> 00:10:50,113
<i>I can feel courage welling up.</i>

124
00:10:52,425 --> 00:10:55,986
<i>I feel that I can hang on,</i>
<i>that I can do it...</i>

125
00:10:57,263 --> 00:11:00,858
<i>that I too am worth something!</i>

126
00:11:04,303 --> 00:11:04,826
Oh!

127
00:11:05,004 --> 00:11:06,164
- No!
- Hinata!

128
00:11:19,085 --> 00:11:19,779
<i>Hinata...</i>

129
00:11:21,587 --> 00:11:23,748
<i>At some point, Hinata, who was</i>
<i>in the habit of just giving up,</i>

130
00:11:24,090 --> 00:11:26,217
<i>made up her mind to change.</i>

131
00:11:29,395 --> 00:11:32,262
<i>Hey, Hinata. It's time to go home.</i>

132
00:11:34,667 --> 00:11:36,794
<i>She put every ounce of</i>
<i>her being into her training.</i>

133
00:11:37,069 --> 00:11:38,764
<i>I saw it with my own eyes.</i>

134
00:11:52,318 --> 00:11:55,151
<i>But even so, she continued</i>
<i>to fail all her missions.</i>

135
00:11:55,955 --> 00:11:57,582
<i>She lost her nerve when</i>
<i>faced with real competition</i>

136
00:11:57,657 --> 00:11:58,885
<i>and became easily discouraged.</i>

137
00:12:01,928 --> 00:12:04,419
<i>But today's Hinata is different.</i>

138
00:12:05,665 --> 00:12:06,927
<i>I have never...</i>

139
00:12:08,100 --> 00:12:10,227
<i>seen...that look in her eyes before.</i>

140
00:12:12,138 --> 00:12:12,968
<i>Naruto.</i>

141
00:12:14,006 --> 00:12:16,941
<i>I have always done</i>
<i>the watching up to now,</i>

142
00:12:18,210 --> 00:12:20,007
<i>but, now, finally...</i>

143
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,572
<i>finally, I am...</i>

144
00:12:23,316 --> 00:12:24,010
<i>Naruto!</i>

145
00:13:09,041 --> 00:13:10,668
You just don't get it, do you?

146
00:13:11,611 --> 00:13:14,375
Your strikes were ineffective
from the very first.

147
00:13:16,315 --> 00:13:17,680
It's the end.

148
00:13:23,422 --> 00:13:25,287
<i>Hinata... That's enough.</i>

149
00:13:26,292 --> 00:13:27,520
<i>You lost the match,</i>

150
00:13:27,593 --> 00:13:29,254
<i>but you've become a new person</i>
<i>in the process.</i>

151
00:13:30,463 --> 00:13:31,555
<i>You did well.</i>

152
00:13:36,269 --> 00:13:38,169
<i>I want to change that about myself...</i>

153
00:13:38,704 --> 00:13:40,001
<i>So I proposed it myself...</i>

154
00:13:45,111 --> 00:13:47,409
Neji's final blow went
straight for the heart.

155
00:13:48,147 --> 00:13:49,045
I feel sorry for her,

156
00:13:49,115 --> 00:13:50,207
but she won't be standing
again now.

157
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:10,261
As further fighting is not feasible
under these conditions...

158
00:14:10,336 --> 00:14:11,098
Don't stop it!

159
00:14:15,408 --> 00:14:16,841
Don't stop the match!
Believe it!

160
00:14:17,243 --> 00:14:18,471
Naruto, stop!

161
00:14:18,744 --> 00:14:20,177
What on earth are you saying, stupid!

162
00:14:20,413 --> 00:14:23,246
She's had it. You can see
she's unconscious...

163
00:14:24,417 --> 00:14:24,974
Huh?

164
00:15:07,793 --> 00:15:09,055
Why do you stand up?

165
00:15:10,663 --> 00:15:13,188
If you continue like this,
you'll really die!

166
00:15:15,234 --> 00:15:16,963
<i>He is now finally for</i>
<i>the first time truly seeing me.</i>

167
00:15:17,837 --> 00:15:19,498
<i>I will not be caught looking bad...</i>

168
00:15:21,674 --> 00:15:22,470
<i>Why?!</i>

169
00:15:24,610 --> 00:15:25,872
<i>In front of...</i>

170
00:15:27,546 --> 00:15:28,570
<i>the person I admire most.</i>

171
00:15:38,858 --> 00:15:40,985
I-I am far from finished!

172
00:15:41,994 --> 00:15:43,518
Give up the bravado...

173
00:15:44,130 --> 00:15:46,963
I can tell you're just
barely standing.

174
00:15:48,834 --> 00:15:50,301
You've shouldered the lot
of having been born

175
00:15:50,369 --> 00:15:52,633
to the head family line of the Hyugan.

176
00:15:54,273 --> 00:15:57,640
And cursed and blamed
yourself for being weak...

177
00:15:58,277 --> 00:16:01,110
But, people cannot change.

178
00:16:01,881 --> 00:16:03,041
That's just the way it is.

179
00:16:04,116 --> 00:16:05,583
There is no need for you
to suffer any more!

180
00:16:06,118 --> 00:16:07,107
Surrender to it!

181
00:16:10,156 --> 00:16:12,556
You're wrong... Brother Neji.

182
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:16,428
Because I can tell...

183
00:16:17,596 --> 00:16:21,327
that you are suffering
much more than I.

184
00:16:22,034 --> 00:16:22,659
What?!

185
00:16:23,002 --> 00:16:25,368
You are the one who is torn up

186
00:16:26,772 --> 00:16:30,264
over the fate of head
and branch family.

187
00:16:37,283 --> 00:16:39,342
Neji, the match has been called!

188
00:16:40,586 --> 00:16:41,177
<i>Oh boy!</i>

189
00:16:52,498 --> 00:16:54,261
Neji, get a hold of yourself!

190
00:16:54,834 --> 00:16:56,631
You promised me

191
00:16:56,702 --> 00:16:58,966
you wouldn't let the head family
thing get you riled up!

192
00:16:59,205 --> 00:17:01,696
Why are all the other Jonin
butting in?!

193
00:17:02,308 --> 00:17:03,866
The head family gets
special treatment, eh?

194
00:17:08,748 --> 00:17:09,339
Hinata?!

195
00:17:10,282 --> 00:17:10,839
Hinata!

196
00:17:11,183 --> 00:17:11,877
Hinata!

197
00:17:12,051 --> 00:17:12,710
Hinata!

198
00:17:15,287 --> 00:17:16,754
Hinata! Are you okay?!

199
00:17:17,156 --> 00:17:17,952
Hey!

200
00:17:20,893 --> 00:17:21,655
Naruto...

201
00:17:22,261 --> 00:17:22,750
Yeah.

202
00:17:26,665 --> 00:17:27,256
I...

203
00:17:35,041 --> 00:17:35,871
<i>Do you think...</i>

204
00:17:39,245 --> 00:17:43,648
<i>I...changed maybe a little bit?</i>

205
00:17:46,986 --> 00:17:49,147
Hey you, failure!

206
00:17:51,557 --> 00:17:53,752
I have two pieces
of advice for you.

207
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,052
First, if you intend to
call yourself a Shinobi,

208
00:17:56,128 --> 00:17:58,028
stop that revolting cheering of yours.

209
00:17:59,398 --> 00:18:00,763
And the second...

210
00:18:01,934 --> 00:18:04,494
a failure will always be a failure.

211
00:18:05,104 --> 00:18:06,366
There's no changing that!

212
00:18:10,009 --> 00:18:11,408
Do you want to see about that?

213
00:18:22,955 --> 00:18:23,580
You!

214
00:18:24,223 --> 00:18:26,714
Naruto, I get where you're
coming from, believe me.

215
00:18:27,626 --> 00:18:31,118
But all fighting must be
done officially in a match!

216
00:18:32,898 --> 00:18:36,425
The failure beats the gifted genius
through sheer effort...

217
00:18:37,470 --> 00:18:39,301
Wouldn't that make for
an exciting main battle?

218
00:18:40,005 --> 00:18:43,600
Though, I am probably going
to be the one fighting Neji...

219
00:18:45,077 --> 00:18:48,877
but it would be okay with me
if you ended up fighting him, Naruto.

220
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:55,687
All right already.

221
00:18:59,959 --> 00:19:01,722
<i>So this is okay then,</i>
<i>right, Guy Sensei?</i>

222
00:19:03,362 --> 00:19:05,159
<i>Lee! You...</i>

223
00:19:06,565 --> 00:19:07,657
<i>Nice going!</i>

224
00:19:22,848 --> 00:19:25,078
<i>Oh, no! She's gone into ventricular fibrillation.</i>

225
00:19:27,453 --> 00:19:28,852
<i>Was he trying to kill her then?!</i>

226
00:19:29,221 --> 00:19:31,382
The precious little time you have
would be better spent

227
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:33,717
seeing to her than glaring at me.

228
00:19:34,059 --> 00:19:34,718
Medics!

229
00:19:34,793 --> 00:19:36,192
Hurry! What's taking so long

230
00:19:36,629 --> 00:19:37,561
S-Sorry.

231
00:19:39,665 --> 00:19:42,225
Get her on the stretcher.
One, two, three.

232
00:19:43,903 --> 00:19:46,098
It's serious. She's got about
10 minutes at the most!

233
00:19:46,305 --> 00:19:48,466
Get her to the emergency room.
Pronto!

234
00:19:48,841 --> 00:19:49,671
Out of the way!

235
00:20:09,929 --> 00:20:10,987
Hinata...

236
00:20:28,547 --> 00:20:31,607
<i>Because that's my Way of Ninja.</i>

237
00:20:38,824 --> 00:20:40,382
<i>I promise you.</i>

238
00:21:00,346 --> 00:21:01,870
I will win no matter what!

239
00:21:06,763 --> 00:21:11,223
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

240
00:21:11,368 --> 00:21:19,707
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

241
00:21:20,710 --> 00:21:29,379
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

242
00:21:29,786 --> 00:21:37,625
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

243
00:21:38,895 --> 00:21:44,299
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

244
00:21:44,367 --> 00:21:48,394
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

245
00:21:48,471 --> 00:21:52,032
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

246
00:21:52,375 --> 00:22:00,908
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

247
00:22:01,184 --> 00:22:06,383
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

248
00:22:06,456 --> 00:22:10,859
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

249
00:22:10,927 --> 00:22:14,693
<i>Just sing.</i>

250
00:22:14,931 --> 00:22:20,096
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

251
00:22:20,170 --> 00:22:22,365
<i>The two are one</i>

252
00:22:22,472 --> 00:22:28,741
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

253
00:22:29,245 --> 00:22:34,342
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

254
00:22:38,201 --> 00:22:39,600
The Absolute Defense of the Sand?

255
00:22:39,869 --> 00:22:42,360
They say no one has
ever injured Gaara.

256
00:22:42,738 --> 00:22:44,933
He's strong as heck and
has no weak points.

257
00:22:45,174 --> 00:22:46,334
Bushy-Brows is no match for him...

258
00:22:46,876 --> 00:22:49,310
But wait, he's not losing

259
00:22:49,579 --> 00:22:51,274
He seems a lot faster than before.

260
00:22:51,447 --> 00:22:53,108
Is this due to his training?

261
00:22:53,216 --> 00:22:55,275
I am getting excited about it!

262
00:22:56,018 --> 00:22:59,954
Next episode: "Gaara vs. Rock Lee:
The Power of Youth Explodes!"

263
00:23:00,323 --> 00:23:03,292
I'm just a little envious of that training.
